<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361465>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Male genitalia: Metapocyrtus (Trachycyrtus) baltazarae, (A–E), Metapocyrtus (Trachycyrtus) siargaonon, (F–I). Aedeagus, dorsal view (A, F), idem, lateral view (B, G), sternite IX, dorsal view (C, H), endophallus in lateral view (F, G, I). In Fig. 3E the profile of the left basal diverticulum has been highlighted to allow a correct view of its morphology." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361465/files/figure.png" ;
